Adjusted regression for resistance outcomes and cognate antibiotic exposure

Kyle Gontjes

2025-05-30

Environment

Load data

tr <- read.tree("./data/tree/tree.treefile")      
df <- readRDS("./data/dataset/df.RDS")

Curate exposures

rownames(df) <- df$isolate_no   
cognate_drugs <- c("bactrim_1d","AG_1d","gent_1d","amikacin_1d","poly_colistin_1d","carbapenem_1d")

# Create factor variables to help regression 
factor_vars_df <- df %>% select(cognate_drugs) %>% as.data.frame()

# convert "yes"  "no" and 10
factor_vars_df <- apply(factor_vars_df,2,FUN=function(x){
  ifelse(x=="yes",1,ifelse(x=="no",0,x)) %>% as.numeric
}) %>% as.data.frame %>% `rownames<-`(df$isolate_no)

# List of resistance columns to convert to factor
drugs <- c("TMP_SMX","gentamicin","AMK","CST","blbli")
phenotypes <- c(paste0(drugs,"_dich_num"))

# Convert specified columns to factor
resistance <- df %>% select(phenotypes) %>% mutate_all(as.factor) 

df_fin <- cbind.data.frame(resistance,factor_vars_df,df %>% select(isolate_no,Patient_ID,Cx_date,age,sex))
# Load asr
pheno <- c("TMP_SMX","gentamicin","AMK","CST","blbli")
for(i in pheno){
  assign(paste0(i,"_asr_clustering"),readRDS(paste0("./data/asr_clustering/",i,"_asr_clustering.RDS")))
}

# Create dataset
for(i in pheno){
  asr_df <- get(paste0(i,"_asr_clustering"))
  df_w_asr <- df_fin %>% left_join(asr_df %>% mutate(isolate_no = child_name))
  assign(paste0(i,"_regression_df"),df_w_asr)
}

LR analyses

Modeling

TMP_SMX_lr <- phyloaware_regression("TMP_SMX_dich_num",df = TMP_SMX_regression_df,variables = c("age",'sex',"bactrim_1d"),first_present = T,patient_id = 'Patient_ID',culture_date = "Cx_date",multivariable = 'multivariable')

gentamicin_lr <- phyloaware_regression("gentamicin_dich_num",gentamicin_regression_df,variables = c("age",'sex',"AG_1d"),first_present = T,patient_id = 'Patient_ID',culture_date = "Cx_date",multivariable = 'multivariable')   

AMK_lr <- phyloaware_regression("AMK_dich_num",AMK_regression_df,variables = c("age",'sex',"AG_1d"),first_present = T,patient_id = 'Patient_ID',culture_date = "Cx_date",multivariable = 'multivariable')

CST_lr <- phyloaware_regression("CST_dich_num",CST_regression_df,variables = c("age",'sex',"poly_colistin_1d"), first_present = T,patient_id = 'Patient_ID',culture_date = "Cx_date",multivariable = 'multivariable')

blbli_lr <- phyloaware_regression("blbli_dich_num",blbli_regression_df,variables = c("age",'sex',"carbapenem_1d"),first_present = T,patient_id = 'Patient_ID',culture_date = "Cx_date",multivariable = 'multivariable')

Generate descriptive stats

TMP_SMX_descriptive <- generate_descriptive_stats("TMP_SMX",TMP_SMX_lr$datasets,variables = "bactrim_1d",factorVars = "bactrim_1d")
TMP_SMX_results <- get_mv_table_adjusted(descriptives = TMP_SMX_descriptive,lr_results=TMP_SMX_lr$multivariable)   

gentamicin_descriptive <- generate_descriptive_stats("gentamicin",gentamicin_lr$datasets,"AG_1d",factorVars = "AG_1d")
gentamicin_results <- get_mv_table_adjusted(descriptives = gentamicin_descriptive,lr_results=gentamicin_lr$multivariable)

AMK_descriptive <- generate_descriptive_stats("AMK",AMK_lr$datasets,"AG_1d",factorVars = "AG_1d")
AMK_results <- get_mv_table_adjusted(descriptives = AMK_descriptive,lr_results=AMK_lr$multivariable)

CST_descriptive <- generate_descriptive_stats("CST",CST_lr$datasets,"poly_colistin_1d",factorVars = "poly_colistin_1d")
CST_results <- get_mv_table_adjusted(descriptives = CST_descriptive,lr_results=CST_lr$multivariable)

blbli_descriptive <- generate_descriptive_stats("blbli",blbli_lr$datasets,"carbapenem_1d",factorVars = "carbapenem_1d")
blbli_results <- get_mv_table_adjusted(descriptives = blbli_descriptive, lr_results=blbli_lr$multivariable)

Forest plot

tabletext <- get_table_text(TMP_SMX_results,gentamicin_results,AMK_results,CST_results,blbli_results)
fp_rmetadata <- get_fp_rmetadata(TMP_SMX_results,gentamicin_results,AMK_results,CST_results,blbli_results)

forest_plot <- res_forest_plot(tabletext = tabletext,fp_rmetadata = fp_rmetadata,outcome_name="Cognate antibiotic",type_of_regression="Adjusted")
